
** Fedora 15

*** Install

  yum update
  yum install gcc
  yum install kernel-headers kernel-devel

  reboot

  yum install xterm
  yum install emacs

** Emacs

  yum groupinstall "X Software Development"
  yum install ncurses-devel
  yum install gtk3-devel.x86_64
  yum install gtk2-devel.x86_64

** Others

  yum install cvs
